nly two sites and one mode we deduce the according effective theory\nfor the two-site Hubbard model coupled to one photonic mode. This model system\nis used to illustrate the basic ideas of a density-functional reformulation in\ngreat detail and we present the exact Kohn-Sham potentials for our coupled\nmatter-photon model system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Mar 2014 18:49:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
